00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:03.130
So what I'd like to do
is to try and just--

00:01:03.130 --> 00:01:06.510
is to get to know you
guys a small little bit.

00:01:06.510 --> 00:01:08.410
And I was thinking
about this last night,

00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:12.460
and it will help me to
make some of my points

00:01:12.460 --> 00:01:15.280
